	<Title>
		Mononucleosis and Epstein-Barr: What&apos;s the connection?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Epstein-Barr virus sometimes causes mononucleosis, but most Epstein-Barr infections are less severe.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		What&apos;s the connection between mononucleosis and Epstein-Barr virus?
	</Question>
